article_title: Rival Gaza protest groups clash on LA campus
sentence: Tensions  flared  at  US  universities  after  the  7  October  Hamas  attack,  in  which  about  1,200  people  were  killed  in  Israel,  and  the  retaliatory  Israeli  military  assault  that  has  killed  more  than  34,000  people  in  Gaza.
